title.rendered: Paradigm leads $20M funding round for Ellipsis Labs’ DeFi expansion

content.rendered: Crypto exchange developer Ellipsis Labs secured $20M in Series A funding led by Paradigm. Electric Capital also participated. The funding will boost their DeFi tech stack and Solana-based DEX, Phoenix.
